chess-world-pi/
├── index.html                 ← Main entry point (loads board, scripts, sounds)
│
├── style/                     ← All CSS styles go here
│   └── style-board.css        ← Board layout, piece colors, toggle styles
│
├── logic/                     ← JavaScript game logic
│   └── logic-board.js         ← Handles piece movement, sounds, toggles
│
├── assets/                    ← All static assets like sounds/images
│   ├── move-sound.mp3         ← Sound when piece moves
│   ├── win-sound.mp3          ← (future: for game win)
│   └── knight-neigh.mp3       ← (future: knight sound effect)
│
├── logo.png                   ← Logo shown at top (optional now)
